Top actress, Stella Damasus is a beauty to behold any day. The actress was on top of the world during the week as she joined the league of celebrities that have turned 40. She shared stunning photos to celebrate her day. Damasus is one actress who hasn't aged a day since she debuted in Nollywood. She's also a singer, having honed her singing skills at Klink Studios, owned by filmmaker, Kingsley Ogoro. She has paid her dues, and she knows it. In her Instagram post, she wrote, "40 ain't easy my niccuh! I deserve some accolades. God's been good to me. Grateful for another year! Stepping into the next phase of my life." Damasus released stunning photographs on social media to celebrate her birthday.